text.section:
The Director of the Center shall:
Report through the Medical System Corporation Chief Executive Officer to the Board of Directors;
Provide a monthly report to the Board of Directors and the EMS Board on the overall progress of programs;
Render reports to appropriate committees of the Board of Directors; and
Develop the budget and, after approval of the Medical System Corporation Chief Executive Officer, present the budget to the EMS Board for review and comment and through the appropriate committees of the Board of Directors for approval by the Board of Directors.
